{"tid":201514,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[求指點]冇愛情冇朋友，咁人生係為左乜野？","createTime":"2017-04-14T19:33:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T08:19:24.000Z","uid":85061,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aba5f8ff1fe96e160af6fe3736f84379e511e551","tid":201514,"uid":85061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T19:33:36.000Z","msg":"畢業之後，每日朝9晚7, 返到屋企都8點幾，大學d朋友都有自己生活，愈來愈少聯絡。<br />\n每日除左返工放工食飯玩手機訓教，就無其他活動。<br />\n想揾個人拍拖？grad左之後仲邊有女仔單身，而且冇左青春，仲邊可以好似以前咁日日對住培養感情，見到而家d學生真係好羡慕，好後悔以前唔識諗放棄左好幾次機會。<br />\n<br />\n想問下大家<br />\n人地返工揾錢係為左家庭，冇家庭咁返工揾錢係為左咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">24A0, 俾人話唔正常(唔係講樣)</span></span>"},{"pid":"5edfe80b53d0b9444305ffa56645b59bddd4b55d","tid":201514,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T19:47:46.000Z","msg":"搵個興趣啦巴打"},{"pid":"5c97ec2e8d7062878b323bb5c2f213927bd1ed13","tid":201514,"uid":90247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T19:49:22.000Z","msg":"努力搵錢買樓 有樓有女 有樓有高潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f495622346bedd726bad14cf4bd9f1dfa95637e5","tid":201514,"uid":99051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T19:51:20.000Z","msg":"我都好驚我會24a0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2008ba355ec3c50c8a758db620455814b21eb14","tid":201514,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T19:52:14.000Z","msg":"如果要有女先有世藝 <br />\n有女先搵到工作嘅動力<br />\n一齊左都好快散 因為你個人無聊<br />\n而且你都會唔適應 <br />\n因為真係愛你嘅女仔好需要人陪<br />\n而你過慣左自己一個人嘅生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583eb38a134970cd844afbf16d7ad